{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Gamepad API","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API\">Gamepad API</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Guides</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API/Using_the_Gamepad_API\">Using the Gamepad API</a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Games/Techniques/Controls_Gamepad_API\">Implementing controls using the Gamepad API</a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\"><code>Gamepad</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/GamepadButton\"><code>GamepadButton</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent\"><code>GamepadEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getGamepads\"><code>Navigator.getGamepads()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepadconnected_event\"><code>Window</code>: <code>gamepadconnected</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepaddisconnected_event\"><code>Window</code>: <code>gamepaddisconnected</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>게임패드 API</strong>는 게임패드와 다른 게임 제어장치의 신호에 쉬운 일관된 방식으로 접근하고 응답하는 개발자들을 위한 수단이다. 게임패드 API는 세 가지 인터페이스와연결, 연결 해제되고 게임 패드 자체에 대한 다른 정보에 접근하고 어떤 버튼과 다른 조작 장치들이 현재 눌린 것에 응답하는 두 가지 이벤트 그리고 한 가지 특수 기능이 포함되어 있다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"인터페이스","title":"인터페이스","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"gamepad_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\"><code>Gamepad</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>컴퓨터에 연결된 게임패드나 조작장치를 표현한다.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"gamepadbutton_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GamepadButton\"><code>GamepadButton</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>연결된 조작장치들 중 하나에 있는 버튼을 표현한다.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"gamepadevent_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent\"><code>GamepadEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>게임 패드와 연관된 이벤트를 나타내는 이벤트 객체이다.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"게임패드_확장기능_실험","title":"게임패드 확장기능 실험","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"gamepadhapticactuator_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GamepadHapticActuator\"><code>GamepadHapticActuator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Represents hardware in the controller designed to provide haptic feedback to the user (if available), most commonly vibration hardware.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"gamepadpose_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GamepadPose\"><code>GamepadPose</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Represents the pose of a controller (e.g. position and orientation in 3D space) in the case of a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">WebVR (en-US)</a> controller.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>\n<p>다음 정보를엑세스할 수 있는 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">게임패드 인터페이스 확장기능 (en-US)</a> 더보기</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"다른_인터페이스로_확장","title":"다른 인터페이스로 확장","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"navigator\">Navigator</h4>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"navigator.getgamepads_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getGamepads\"><code>Navigator.getGamepads()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>An extension to the <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a> object that returns an array of <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\"><code>Gamepad</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> objects, one for each connected gamepad.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>\n<h4 id=\"window_events\">Window events</h4>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"window.ongamepadconnected_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepadconnected_event\"><code>Window.ongamepadconnected</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Represents an event handler that will run when a gamepad is connected (when the <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepadconnected_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">gamepadconnected (en-US)</a></code> event fires).</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"window.ongamepaddisconnected_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepaddisconnected_event\"><code>Window.ongamepaddisconnected</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Represents an event handler that will run when a gamepad is disconnected (when the <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepaddisconnected_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">gamepaddisconnected (en-US)</a></code> event fires).</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"튜토리얼과_가이드","title":"튜토리얼과 가이드","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API/Using_the_Gamepad_API\">Using the Gamepad API</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Techniques/Controls_Gamepad_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Implementing controls using the Gamepad API (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"사양","title":"사양","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Specification</th>\n      <th>Status</th>\n      <th>Comment</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/gamepad/extensions.html\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'Gamepad Extensions' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">Gamepad Extensions</a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-ed\">Editor's Draft</span></td>\n      <td>Defines the <a href=\"#experimental_gamepad_extensions\">Experimental Gamepad extensions</a>.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/gamepad/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Gamepad<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'The Gamepad API specification' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n      <td>Initial definition</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성","isH3":false,"query":"api.Gamepad","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"더보기","title":"더보기","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://hacks.mozilla.org/2013/12/the-gamepad-api/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">The Gamepad API</a> by Ted Mielczarek and Robert Nyman</li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://luser.github.io/gamepadtest/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Simple API demo page</a> (<a href=\"https://github.com/luser/gamepadtest\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">source</a>)</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"인터페이스","id":"인터페이스"},{"text":"튜토리얼과 가이드","id":"튜토리얼과_가이드"},{"text":"사양","id":"사양"},{"text":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성"},{"text":"더보기","id":"더보기"}],"summary":"게임패드 API는 게임패드와 다른 게임 제어장치의 신호에 쉬운 일관된 방식으로 접근하고 응답하는 개발자들을 위한 수단이다. 게임패드 API는 세 가지 인터페이스와연결, 연결 해제되고 게임 패드 자체에 대한 다른 정보에 접근하고 어떤 버튼과 다른 조작 장치들이 현재 눌린 것에 응답하는 두 가지 이벤트 그리고 한 가지 특수 기능이 포함되어 있다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/gamepad_api","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/gamepad_api/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API","title":"Gamepad API"}],"pageTitle":"Gamepad API - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}